flowchart TD
  A[Need expertise or repeated capability] --> B{High-risk one-off decision?}
  B -- yes --> C[Assign SME review]
  B -- no --> D{Recurring across teams?}
  D -- yes --> E[Design COE mode]
  D -- no --> F[Keep local team ownership]
  C --> G[Name decision owner and risk owner]
  E --> H[Choose advisory, enablement, platform, governance, or community mode]
  G --> I[Record recommendation, evidence, and exception path]
  H --> J[Create reusable assets and adoption metrics]
  I --> K[Review outcome and reduce dependency]
  J --> K
  K --> L{Capability normalized?}
  L -- yes --> M[Federate or sunset]
  L -- no --> N[Adjust scope, support, and decision rights]
  N --> K
